content.rendered:
Directed by Kaustav Narayan Niyogi. Gill Shubham. Cast . Akshay Anan. Richa Chadh. Gulshan Devaia. Gulshan Grove. Sharad S. Kapoo. Rajat Kau. Manoj Pahw. Sheeva Ran. Rahul Ro. Sujata Sanghamitr. Vipin Sharm.

Cast Akshay Anand(Victor (Roza’s Manager)). Richa Chadha(Roza’Rajshri’). Gulshan Devaiah(Gaurav). Gulshan Grover(Don Salim). Sharad S. Kapoor(Vikram Batwal). Rajat Kaul(Nawaab). Manoj Pahwa(Newspaper owner). Sheeva Rana(Meera). Rahul Roy(Self). Sujata Sanghamitra(Neena (Gaurav’s boss)). Vipin Sharma(Police Inspector). Bhavya Shinde(Main Friend of Gulshan Devaiah). S. Sreesanth(Chetta Don). Olivia M Williams(Dancer)

Language Hindi.

Producers Pooja Bhatt. Himanshu Joshi. Bhushan Kumar. Rahul Mittra. Yogiraj Shetty.

Production Fish Eye Network. T-Series.
